name: Daily work route
description: This is my daily work route. I live in the city of Jakarta, in Indonesia. I am a lecturer in visual communication design. Every day I change universities to teach. I go by motorbike to work. Daily work route (in English: means Daily work route). In this illustration I describe the hardships of working as a lecturer. Traffic jams and fulfilling all kinds of obligations as a lecturer in Indonesia. Here I describe that I started my work by departing from my house in the Taman Palem Lestari area of Jakarta
